		<div class="question-answer">
			<h2 class="question" id="question">How are you supposed to pass a float serve? </h2>
			
			<h2 class="explanation" id="explanation">If you wait to pass a float serve with your forearm it will be really difficult to predict where it is going, so the best thing to do is pass it before it gets close to the floor, this means passing it with the fingertips.</h2>
		</div>
		
		<div class="answers">
			<div class="answer1" id="answer1">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer1-text">Stay a bit forward where you would pass the ball and pass it using your finger tips</h3>
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer2" id="answer2">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer2-text">Hit it back using one of your hands palm </h3>
			</div>
			
			
			<div class="answer3" id="answer3">
				
				
				<h3 class = "answer3-text">Wait until you see where is the ball going and pass it using your arms</h3>
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer4" id="answer4">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer4-text">Pass it using your arms slowing the ball down , as it already has enough power to go to the setter </h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		
